上映的首个周末在中国获得5千5百万美元的票房。<ref name= Lang>{{cite web|url= http://variety.com/2015/film/box-office/star-wars-force-awakens-box-office-2-1201668081/|title= ‘Star Wars’ Leads Foreign Box Office for Second Straight Week|author= Brent Lang|date= December 27, 2015|accessdate= December 28, 2015|work= [[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|archive-date= 2021-01-31|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20210131045847/https://variety.com/2015/film/box-office/star-wars-force-awakens-box-office-2-1201668081/|dead-url= no}}</ref>最终累计6.49亿元人民币。

